public override func decode(_: Int32): SinglePrecisionFloat {
        var bits: Int32 = 0
        bits |= nextSymbol() & 0xFF
        bits <<= 8
        bits |= nextSymbol() & 0xFF
        bits <<= 8
        bits |= nextSymbol() & 0xFF
        bits <<= 8
        bits |= nextSymbol() & 0xFF
        return SinglePrecisionFloat(Float32.fromBits(UInt32(bits)))
    }
